      • methodTable

        public VMMethod[] methodTable
        Methods declared in this class, plus any abstract virtual methods inherited from implemented or extended interfaces. If addendum is non-null and addendum.declaredMethodCount is non-negative, then the first addendum.declaredMethodCount methods are declared methods, while the rest are abstract virtual methods. If addendum is null or addendum.declaredMethodCount is negative, all are declared methods.
